$$
f_n(Î¸_j) = âˆ‘_{k=0}^{n-1} \hat f_k^n {\rm e}^{{\rm i} k Î¸_j} = \sqrt n ğ_j^âŠ¤ Q_n^â‹† \vchatf^n = ğ_j^âŠ¤ Q_n^â‹† Q_n ğŸ^n = f(Î¸_j).
$$

